commits.content:
[book]
title = "Porting ggen from clap to clap-noun-verb"
description = "A comprehensive guide for porting the ggen CLI application from regular clap to clap-noun-verb framework"
authors = ["clap-noun-verb contributors"]
language = "en"
multilingual = false
src = "src"

[build]
create-missing = true

[rust]
edition = "2021"
# Disable rustdoc testing for documentation examples
no-default-features = false
# Don't treat code blocks as testable unless explicitly marked
test = false

[output.html]
git-repository-url = "https://github.com/seanchatmangpt/clap-noun-verb"
edit-url-template = "https://github.com/seanchatmangpt/clap-noun-verb/edit/main/docs/book/{path}"

[output.html.search]
enable = true
limit-results = 30
teaser-word-count = 30
use-boolean-and = true
boost-title = 2
boost-hierarchy = 1
boost-paragraph = 1
expand = true
heading-split-level = 3
copy-button = true
snippet-length = 30
